description:
The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills returns and Danny is here to recap the season. The premiere features Bamboozle Jayne, Crystal's debut, Kathy's child dentistry, and lots more! Danny also briefly touches on the RHONJ feud between Melissa and Jennifer that's brewing alongside the reunion!


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
